1. Font Choice

    *Note : Donot Choose Fonts More than Two For a Website

    Type 1 : Serif 

        Times New Roman
        Palatino Linotype
        Georgia

    Type 2 : Sans Serif

        Arial
        Helvetica Neue
        Tahoma
    
2. Size

    14px to 16px (Suggested Size)

3. Line Height

    *Note : Set the line height at approximately 150% of body text size.

    For example : 14px text size works well at 21px (150%)  of line height.  

4. Alingment
5. Readablility

